## Project structure

```
{{PROJECT_NAME}}-api-tester/
├── CLAUDE.local.md               # This file
├── .claude/
│   └── rules/
│       ├── curl-workflow.md      # Curl paste workflow
│       └── api-testing.md        # API testing notes
├── config/
│   ├── environments.json         # baseUrl + canExecute per env
│   ├── state.json                # activeEnvironment + lastRequest (git-ignored)
│   └── tokens/                   # bearer tokens per env (git-ignored)
├── reference/
│   └── api-endpoints.json        # known endpoints catalog
├── scripts/
│   ├── request.sh                # main request runner (persists req + res)
│   ├── parse-curl.sh             # curl parser helper
│   ├── generate-postman.sh       # Postman exporter
│   ├── analyze.js                # large-response summariser
│   └── slice.js                  # JS-filter slicer
├── requests/
│   └── <env>/                    # request body + _meta per call (git-ignored)
├── responses/
│   ├── <env>/                    # pretty JSON responses per env (git-ignored)
│   └── sliced/                   # filtered subsets (reusable)
└── postman/                      # generated Postman collections
```

